WEBVTT

00:06:29.676 --> 00:06:33.737
to ramp up the production of military airplanes,

00:06:33.737 --> 00:06:37.271
we should be able to do something similar

00:06:37.271 --> 00:06:40.978
to tackle the HIV/AIDS epidemic.

00:06:40.978 --> 00:06:43.041
And we did.

00:06:43.041 --> 00:06:48.430
In 2010, UNITAID established the Medicines Patent Pool

00:06:48.430 --> 00:06:51.913
for HIV.

00:06:51.913 --> 00:06:53.542
And this is how it works:

00:06:53.542 --> 00:06:57.213
Patent holders, inventors

00:06:57.213 --> 00:07:01.058
that develop new medicines